@startuml "Transaction State Machine"

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam shadowing false

title Checkout Transaction State Machine

state "STARTED" as S : Generate tx_id\nPersist tx log entry\nwith order details
state "RESERVING_STOCK" as RS : XADD stock-commands\n{tx_id, cmd=RESERVE_STOCK, items}\nWait for tx-response (timeout)
state "DEDUCTING_PAYMENT" as DP : XADD payment-commands\n{tx_id, cmd=DEDUCT_PAYMENT, user_id, amount}\nWait for tx-response (timeout)
state "COMPENSATING_STOCK" as CS : XADD stock-commands\n{tx_id, cmd=COMPENSATE_STOCK, items}\nWait for tx-response (timeout)
state "COMPLETED" as C #LightGreen : Mark order.paid = true\nTerminal state
state "ABORTED" as A #Salmon : Order stays unpaid\nTerminal state

[*] --> S : POST /checkout/{order_id}

S --> RS : persist state\nthen publish command

RS --> DP : SUCCESS\npersist state\nthen publish command
RS --> A : FAILURE\n(no compensation needed)
RS --> RS : TIMEOUT\n(retry, idempotent)

DP --> C : SUCCESS\nmark order paid
DP --> CS : FAILURE\n(must compensate stock)
DP --> DP : TIMEOUT\n(retry, idempotent)

CS --> A : SUCCESS\n(stock restored)
CS --> CS : TIMEOUT\n(retry until success\ncompensation must complete)

C --> [*]
A --> [*]

note right of RS
  On **Order service restart**:
  scan tx log for non-terminal states,
  re-enter state machine at recorded state
end note

note right of CS
  Compensation **must eventually succeed**.
  Retry indefinitely with backoff.
end note

@enduml
